{"tid":1714153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港島線至為重要","createTime":"2019-11-12T23:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T00:48:03.000Z","uid":230825,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0234aab51bb859a178072c223c1f3dcae999ac34","tid":1714153,"uid":230825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:56:52.000Z","msg":"中環金鐘呢啲中心商業區嘅地鐵站一定唔可以比啲暴徒塞住架<br />\n塞咗就好多大公司無得開工架喇<br />\n你哋啲暴徒啊 搞還搞啊 唔好整到港島線都停埋啊<br />\n已經無晒過海巴士架喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3a3fa3ff3b61f48ef617e6c361d1a4bbbf1180","tid":1714153,"uid":230825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:57:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a1d73b0b8493f51ac960efa976c129256bdc3c2c","tid":1714153,"uid":212646,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:57:26.000Z","msg":"港島手足我求你地出黎塞鐵呀"},{"pid":"4feaca4c4033ed8a6adc176bcf47d9a9065371f7","tid":1714153,"uid":173640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:57:37.000Z","msg":"齊齊去塞港島綫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470f5a7b8c16311ea6e185456716422ccceae654","tid":1714153,"uid":10038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:58:07.000Z","msg":"好多人仲上到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86476746688e105adcdf9cf18957c99c1f03387","tid":1714153,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:58:25.000Z","msg":"推逃生門"},{"pid":"a4004add00353e1f25a985df49c7f77b1450bda5","tid":1714153,"uid":22589,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:58:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好焚毀港島線 我要返工</span>"},{"pid":"f7cd0d10fde7e7871f4b7dc2d9df899015d18db0","tid":1714153,"uid":230825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:03:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b90f073e5fa1adc954112549663edc2dc6612cd3","tid":1714153,"uid":230825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:04:02.000Z","msg":"香港島啊！"},{"pid":"73bf770cec1dee2ef7e3d0dd548b7addaf955aed","tid":1714153,"uid":273188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"（緊急）點解之前死都唔肯停課，昨天停曬八大，之後就暴力清場，好明顯政府認為滅左你大學生，事件就會完，<br />\n所有其它大學要作最壞打算，準備可以立即徹離，唔可以比人圍困<br />\n對無人性的林鄭來說，唔好誤以為停課係為你地安全着想，佢係想暴力清場。<br />\n仲有，有消息內地生徹走，好明顯為屠殺鋪路<br />\n必須推上國際，要話比世界聽&ldquo;天安門事件&rdquo;又即將發生，仲要係警察想走入八大，消滅整個世代的大學生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1712238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1712238</a>"},{"pid":"1e4f22690ac136be126af0f09a7493501ce8cc5a","tid":1714153,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fc05f2e16aa39633cc42a724b0a35aab01cfb7","tid":1714153,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"做緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973249d45d119cacd14b1e77d64b3858fec7dd52","tid":1714153,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88597cdce23d8df0b0b572f96a081700e52c59b2","tid":1714153,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:34:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47a9bd7db50ad2b98d8996774342094d6186fe25","tid":1714153,"uid":25071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:34:50.000Z","msg":"［最後召集］港島線朝朝都唔夠人幫手 出嚟啦港島人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1714071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1714071</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dca1adced56e624e48786654364aa49b4f33cd58","tid":1714153,"uid":44925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:35